data.description: This Spacious Victorian has 3 Bedrooms/2 Baths, 3/4 Walk Down Basement, Great Floor Plan, main level has been  sheet rocked and has new wiring however upstairs there is still lathe and plaster and the wiring has not been updated.  There is a large sun porch off the back that walks out to fully fenced backyard.  1 car garage!  One Bathroom on each level.  This property needs some TLC but has the square footage to make a lovely home.  New Woodbridge Windows with lifetime warranty that transfers to new owner. Newer heat and air!
